events.name: 【146】出来心と下心 自動実行

parameters: 3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Clea: Thanks to you, I was saved. I didn't know what could
happen in that rain.

Farmer Apros: It's no problem. Just defeating that beast was
more than enough.

Farmer Apros: I need to let my friend, the hunter, know that
he can hunt without worry now that the beast has been
defeated.
Clea: Didn't you ask the Bulk Gang for help?

Farmer Apros: I'm an outsider who came from Barie, so I
haven't been able to fit in with the people of Valt...

Farmer Apros: Don't make such a serious face! By the way, I
wonder what happened to my friends?

Clea: It seems they headed towards the forest for
exploration since the rain has stopped.

Clea: I was unsure of what to do when it started raining
heavily.

Clea: In the end, I can't accept the reward for the request
if I'm the one being saved by the client.

Farmer Apros: I can't let that happen! You've done a great
job completing the request, haven't you!?
Clea: This is a matter of pride as an adventurer.

Farmer Apros: I understand your conviction. How about
canceling it out with another request...?

Farmer Apros: How about warming up our cold bodies while
we're both soaking wet... Hahaha, what do you think?
order：クレアの淫乱レベルが3の時のみ選択肢表示
Farmer Apros: Ahaha, what a joke--

Clea: If that's the request, I will follow it. This will
also help erase my doubts from this time.
Farmer Apros: Huh... Are you really... okay with it?
Clea: Mr. Apros, please take off your clothes too.

Clea: I understand what it means to warm our cold bodies
together.

Farmer Apros: The bed is not very comfortable, but there is
one in the other room...
Would you like to skip the adult scene?

Farmer Apros: It's a shame that it's only once. Since I'll
be posting a request on the bulletin board, come and visit
again for some fun.

Clea (I should have dismissed that silly joke... Why did
I... and I even seemed to enjoy it...)
Clea: ...If I have the time, I might accept the request.
Clea: Please stop with the jokes.

Farmer Apros: Ahaha, yeah, just kidding! I'll start a fire
now, so wait for me.

Farmer Apros: As an apology for the silly joke, please
accept this reward.
Clea: Understood... I will accept it.

Farmer Apros: ...Half of it was serious. If you change your
mind, take a look at the bulletin board.

Farmer Apros: You were so beautiful when you got wet in the
rain.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Do you want to skip the adult scene?
Farmer Apros: I can't believe you actually came...
Farmer Apros: I still can't believe this situation.
